3\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17478,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/06\/jihad-in-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":34669,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Do you love to strive in supplication?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo you wish to strive in supplication? Say: O Allah, help me to be grateful to You, to remember You, and to worship You in the best manner.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 7982 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21276,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/11\/22\/aisha-best-worship-humility\/","url_meta":{"origin":34669,"position":3},"title":"Aisha on Humility: Among the best acts of worship is humility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Mubarak reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cVerily, you are neglecting the best act of worship: humility.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 391 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0628\u0627\u0631\u0643 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0